results.name: Number of permutations of the multiset of prime factors of n whose first part is not 2.
formula: If n is odd, a(n) = A008480(n). If n is even, a(n) = A008480(n) - A008480(n/2).
example: The a(90) = 9 permutations of {2,3,3,5} not starting with 2:
xref: Number of times n appears in A325390.
